<img src="/content/dam/news-events/news/2019/06/201967-buzzer-beater.jpg" alt="A fan on her knees watching the final basket go in"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>After bouncing on the rim four times, this is the decisive moment when the ball finally dropped.&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>
</div>
						    
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
